  <HelpTopic SearchKey="CreateLPF">
    <Header>Complex numbers</Header>

    <Content>
      <Title>Creating complex numbers</Title>

      <Text>
          i = sqrt (-1);   % pre-defined 
          j = sqrt (-1);   % pre-defined
            a = 3 + 4 * i;
            
          Both i and j can be changed. The will revert to sqrt (-1) 
          after a "clear"

          If both have been changed, complex numbers sqrt (-1)
          can be used
            a = 3 + 4 * sqrt (-1);          
      </Text>
    </Content>
  </HelpTopic>
  
